---

This package incorporates skills derived from upstream Anthropic projects:

- `frontend-design` — copied from anthropics/claude-code/plugins/frontend-design
- `mcp-builder`, `skill-creator` — copied / adapted from anthropics/skills
- `code-review`, `feature-dev`, `code-explorer`, `code-architect`, `code-reviewer`
  — translated from anthropics/claude-code/plugins/{code-review,feature-dev}
- `security-review` — translated from
  anthropics/claude-code-security-review/.claude/commands/security-review.md
- `agents-md-improver` — adapted from
  anthropics/claude-plugins-official/plugins/claude-md-management/skills/claude-md-improver
  (renamed from `claude-md-improver`; covers both AGENTS.md and CLAUDE.md)
- `agents-md-revise` — translated from
  anthropics/claude-plugins-official/plugins/claude-md-management/commands/revise-claude-md.md
  (renamed from `revise-claude-md`; converted from slash command to skill)

Each derived skill includes attribution in its frontmatter `license` field.
The original Anthropic projects are MIT-licensed; see their repositories for
upstream license text.
